See https://rpi4cluster.com/monitoring/k3s-prometheus/
and https://computingforgeeks.com/setup-prometheus-and-grafana-on-kubernetes/

$ kubectl label node n1 n2 n3 n4 n5 node-role.kubernetes.io/worker=true
node/n1 labeled
node/n2 labeled
node/n3 labeled
node/n4 labeled
node/n5 labeled

